---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import EliaPari from "../assets/elia-pari.jpg";
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>

  <body class="ae-body">
    <Header />

    <main class="mb-12 flex-grow">
      <Container size="sm" marginBottom="mb-16">
        <section class="flex flex-col items-center">
          <Image class="mb-8" width={240} height={240} src={EliaPari} alt={SITE_TITLE} />

          <h1 class="mb-6 text-6xl font-bold">{SITE_TITLE}</h1>

          <h2 class="mb-16 text-4xl font-bold">Web Developer</h2>

          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-ae-black"></div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-ae-white"></div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-ae-red"></div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-ae-blue"></div>
          <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-ae-pink"></div>
        </section>
      </Container>

      <Container size="sm">
        <section class="prose prose-ae m-auto dark:prose-invert md:prose-lg lg:prose-xl">
          <h3>Somenthing about this</h3>

          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec vel pretium enim. Aenean nec enim aliquam,
            pharetra elit lobortis, venenatis mauris. Proin luctus gravida risus, non fermentum orci vulputate et.
            Vivamus hendrerit eros quis libero pharetra, ut suscipit metus convallis. Nunc faucibus luctus mattis.
            Suspendisse et mauris mi. Proin suscipit eget risus a pretium. Donec nec elit id felis consequat dapibus
            sagittis quis massa. Etiam vitae scelerisque magna. Phasellus sagittis ultricies odio. Mauris lorem tellus,
            euismod vel viverra ut, lobortis eu eros. Sed fermentum enim vel lacus placerat, eget posuere urna
            porttitor. Aenean non sollicitudin enim. Maecenas porta enim in elementum euismod. Vivamus odio turpis,
            sollicitudin sit amet varius nec, malesuada ut urna.
          </p>
        </section>
      </Container>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
